noUndeclaredEnvVars.option:
Use the options to specify additional environment variables that are not declared inglobalEnv,globalPassThroughEnv, or task-levelenv/passThroughEnvinturbo.json.
Supports regular expression patterns (anchors^and$are implicit).
{  "linter": {    "rules": {      "nursery": {        "noUndeclaredEnvVars": {          "options": {            "allowedEnvVars": [              "MY_APP_.*",              "ACME_TOKEN"            ]          }        }      }    }  }}
